creator: axiom
title: [WIP] axiom MacOS - HRM + ColemakDH
notes:
[Work in Progress]
Axiom Layout - MacOS

Originally based on Miryoku, implemented using the functionality provided by TailorKey, and the Glove80 layout editor's native macro, hold-tap and combo support.

Includes an old symbol layout from my old Moonlander layout. Testing if it still feels good.

Default placements of keys like Home, End, arrows, etc, have been left in place, though they aren't used day to day.
